From: Darrick J. Wong <darrick.wong@oracle.com>

Move the extent size hint checks that aren't xfs-specific to the vfs.

Signed-off-by: Darrick J. Wong <darrick.wong@oracle.com>
Reviewed-by: Jan Kara <jack@suse.cz>
